{"tid":502034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋物]喺機場巴士站漏咗把遮","createTime":"2017-12-17T13:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T09:59:05.000Z","uid":92288,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1979416eb0a02f1d5bb5c4b8674904969a8e07fe","tid":502034,"uid":92288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"人類總要重複同樣的錯誤，唉，今日3點落到機，擺咗行李同掛咗把遮係行李車到，然後狗衝去推到去E21站到搭車，咁就漏咗把遮喺個行李車到<br />\n<br />\n9個字後突然醒起，打咗機場報失熱線，都無消息<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然知無乜機會攞翻，但都駁下，各位巴絲有無見過，全新有掛牌，係韓國買，白柄湖水綠長遮,下圖:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/210522_622e5c307707cd4539ea1c8b8f65af8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F210522_622e5c307707cd4539ea1c8b8f65af8c.jpg&h=847f7248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖案樣:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/210620_c2430a65655c19c474a537bbf7284ed4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F210620_c2430a65655c19c474a537bbf7284ed4.jpg&h=d76f8a1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1de6b8f859b901628809db670564352f15f251ee","tid":502034,"uid":92288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d50d763197956369615f833393d3a698e51c10","tid":502034,"uid":92288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285